JoggerServlet, MockJoggerServlet
public abstract class AbstractJoggerServlet
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet

Support class that acts as a base class for JoggerServlet and MockJoggerServlet providing common functionality. It extends from HttpServlet because Java only allows to extend from one class.

Author:
German Escobar

buildFreeMarker

protected abstract freemarker.template.Configuration buildFreeMarker()
Configure the FreeMarker configuration object. Implementations of this method must, at least, call one of the following: 
        freemarker.setServletContextForTemplateLoading(servletContext, templatesPath);
        // or
        freemarker.setDirectoryForTemplateLoading(new File(templatesPath));
        // or
        freemarker.setClassForTemplateLoading(Some.class, templatesPath);
